{"type": "article", "id": 15526, "title": "Luna 台灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-25T06:30:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 192, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135550bPXDIdaTU7OJlGhY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t许多灯都借用了月亮的元素，这盏月球灯做的更加仿真。模拟了月球表面有适当深浅变化的纹路，在黄色光照下非常温暖。材料选用玻璃纤维与乳胶液，具有抗热、防水的功能。 尺寸从 3.2 英尺到 236 英尺共7种，迷你版的灯是靠电池供电，其他均为插电。来自台湾橡果艺术工作室 Acorn，有没有让你想起几米的《月亮忘记了》？<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/luna-bring-the-moon-along-with-you#/storyBruvelo\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142608atK3IClBuPez9D1S.jpg\" width=\"882\" height=\"588\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261426097kbGJUl3Qu1vV5hW.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142609aXmnAe52y6r4gRoi.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142610PcfNJlDygXounqF2.jpg\" width=\"873\" height=\"582\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}